        id - The player id.

        name - The player's name.
        status - Information about what next action is expected from the player. Possibilities are: spiel starten, wartet auf spielbeginn, dorf bauen, strasse bauen, wuerfeln, handeln oder bauen, warten, verbindung verloren
        victoryPoints - The player's current points.
